About this item

  • Play a card from your hand, and place a chip on a corresponding space on the game board - when you have five in a row, it’s a SEQUENCE

  • Exciting gameplay develops STEM skills like strategy
  • Includes 1 Folding Game Board (19.75" x 15.25"), 2 Decks of SEQUENCE Playing Cards (2.25" x 3.5"), 135 Playing Chips (50 Green, 50 Blue, 35 Red), and Complete Instructions
  • For 2-12 players, ages 7 and up

Product Description

Product Description

It's fun, it's challenging, it's exciting, it's SEQUENCE! Play a card from your hand, and place a chip on a corresponding space on the game board. When you have five in a row, it's a SEQUENCE. Learn to block your opponents or remove their chips, and watch out for the Jacks - they're wild! With a little strategy and luck, you'll be a winner. Includes 1 Folding Game Board (19.75" x 15.25"), 2 Decks of SEQUENCE Playing Cards (2.25" x 3.5"), 135 playing chips: 35 red, 50 blue and 50 green, and Complete Instructions For 2-12 players, ages 7 and up.

From the manufacturer

Goliath SEQUENCE Board Game, Ages 7 and up, 2-12 players

This exciting game of strategy is fun for the whole family - play as individuals or teams!

Play a card from your hand, and place a chip on a corresponding space on the game board - get 5 in a row for a SEQUENCE

Jacks are wild and can be used for any space on the board or to remove an opponent's chip!

The first player or team with the required number of SEQUENCES wins!

Description Play a card from your hand, and place a chip on a corresponding space on the game board. When you have five in a row, it’s a SEQUENCE. Block your opponents or remove their chips. The first player or team with the required number of SEQUENCES wins! This giant-sized SEQUENCE is a great way to enjoy the classic game of strategy with family and friends! Play as teams or individuals on the 27” x 32” durable cushioned playing mat which can be used on the floor or table for big game night fun! It's the exciting game of SEQUENCE just for kids! Play an animal card from your hand, and place your chip on the corresponding animal on the board. The first player with four chips in a row wins! Reading is not required to play. Players sound out the letter on their card, match it to the beginning sound of a picture on the game board, and place a chip there. Wild cards are used to add a chip to an open space or remove an opponent’s chip! Get 4 in a row for a SEQUENCE to win! It's the strategic game of SEQUENCE as an easy to play dice game! Roll the dice and place a chip on a corresponding number on the game board. Get 5 chips in a row and you win! The dice add a fun twist to the game that your whole family will enjoy!

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        5.0 out of 5 stars A Classic Game for Endless Fun!
        Reviewed in the United States on July 29, 2023
        Color: MulticolorVerified Purchase
        SEQUENCE is a timeless and beloved game that brings friends and family together for hours of entertainment. The game comes with a folding board, cards, and chips, providing everything you need to start playing right out of the box.

        The objective of SEQUENCE is simple yet strategic: be the first player or team to complete a sequence of five chips in a row on the game board. Each player or team takes turns playing a card from their hand and placing a chip on the corresponding space on the board. With a combination of luck and skill, players must strategically plan their moves to block opponents and create their own sequences.

        The game is easy to learn, making it suitable for players of all ages, from kids to adults. Its portability and compact size (10.3" x 8.1" x 2.31") make it ideal for family gatherings, game nights, or even taking on the go during trips.

        One of the highlights of SEQUENCE is its ability to accommodate both small and large groups. Whether you're playing one-on-one or in teams, the game remains engaging and exciting, making it a versatile choice for various social settings.

        The packaging of the game may vary, but the contents remain the same, ensuring consistent gameplay and quality regardless of the design.

        As with any game, there are different strategies to master, adding an element of challenge and replayability. SEQUENCE can be enjoyed by players of varying skill levels, making it an inclusive and enjoyable experience for everyone involved.

        One possible enhancement could be introducing more card sets or expansions to provide additional variety and keep long-time players engaged with new challenges.

        In conclusion, SEQUENCE is a classic game that never gets old. Its simplicity, strategy, and endless fun make it a must-have for any game collection. So, gather your friends and family, unfold the board, and get ready for an exciting and memorable game night with SEQUENCE!
